metadata.name: Flow
metadata.description:
This genesis piece is perhaps one of my favorite photographs I have ever made. 
Enjoying the moment, surrounded by nothing more than the roar of rushing water. This frame was captured on a crisp Fall morning in the Canadian Rockies, soon to be covered in snow just a few short days later. 
I hope you enjoy this fleeting moment from Fall 2021 and Sunwapta Falls entitled "Flow."


The collector of this 1 of 1 edition will receive a 23x30 fine art print and the full resolution file.
